## ğŸ” Root User Login (Important Concept)

### âœ… Root User kya hota hai?

Root user:

 Account ka full access owner hota hai
 Sab services, billing, IAM manage kar sakta hai

âš ï¸ Best Practice:

 Daily use ke liye IAM user create karo
 Root account sirf setup & billing ke liye use karo

